::DarkMouse/KitKat::

DarkMouse::
She left Quickstrike for a  moment and went to the console.  She 
pressed a few buttons so that her link will go through the console 
link.  She returned to Quickstrike's side.
She spoke through her link,"Someone will be at your ship shortly."

She closed her link to the strange ship and opened it up to 
KitKat."KitKat, there is a ship at the edge of our boarders.  Can you 
and find out what that impatient bot wants?"

KitKat:;
" Give me the coordinants and I'll go.  Then after all this, can I go 
back and look for Rowdy?"
She hated even asking, but feared getting reported to Megatron more.

DarkMouse::
"Yes, after this you can resume your search. And Thank you."
She used her commlink through the console and sent KitKat the 
directions.
